body.tagline: Create your website with NuxtJS, Storyblok and deploy it on Netlify.
body.headline: NuxtWebsite

columns.name: Nuxt.Js
columns.description: Nuxt.js is a framework for creating Universal Vue.js Applications. It presets all the configuration needed to make your development of a Vue.js Application Server Rendered more enjoyable.

columns.name: Storyblok
columns.description: CMS done right. API based & Headless with clean and structured JSON for you as developer and a CMS your editors will fall in love with. Unlimited extensibility through custom plugins using VueJs.

columns.name: Netlify
columns.description: Build, deploy, and manage modern web projects. Get an all-in-one workflow that combines global deployment, continuous integration, and HTTPS.

columns.name: We should grab a beer
columns.description: Looks like we've now got time for a beer. [Nuxt](https://nuxtjs.org/) will boost your development time, [Storyblok](https://www.storyblok.com/) your content integration and optimization and [Netlify](https://www.netlify.com/) will get you online!

columns.name: Editing without the hussle
columns.description: Use Storybloks [SideBySide Editing Interface](https://www.storyblok.com/feature/visual-composer) to easily manage your components per page and ship pretty new landing pages.

columns.name: Your pagespeed score is low?
columns.description: Simply [add some parameters](https://www.storyblok.com/docs/image-service) to your images and you can resize, crop, greyscale or simply only lower their quality.

columns.name: Create flat and nested content structures
columns.description: Storyblok will allow you to [manage flat content structures](https://www.storyblok.com/feature/content-types) like a blog post or an event, but also [nested components](https://www.storyblok.com/feature/blocks) to build out layouts for landing pages with components you define yourself!

columns.name: Wanna play with us?
columns.description: The best about everything you can see here â€“ you can use it for free. You can find this setup on Github - no strings attached. Netlify and Storyblok both ship with generous free tiers! So what are you waiting for - jump into Nuxt! :)
